
<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html>
     <!-- HEAD -->
    <title>TecnoMundo-Mi carrito</title> 
     <%- include('./partials/head') %>

    </head>
    <body class="body-carrito">
      <!-- HEADER -->
      <%- include('./partials/header') %>
        
      <!-- MAIN -->
    <main class="main-carrito container-detail">
          <div class="shopping-cart">
            <a href="/product/productCart" title=" Tus Compras"><i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping" ></i></a>
            <h1>Mi Carrito</h1>
          </div>
          <Section class="cart-container">
              
          </Section>
          
          <!-- template carrito -->

          <template id="template-carrito">
            <article class="article-margin-padding cart-items">
            <div class="img-items">
              <img src="images/Celulares/1.jpg" alt="imagen-item-1">
            </div>
            <div class="description-item">
              <h4 class="name">Nombre</h4>
              <h4 class="description h4-carrito">Motorola Moto E7 Plus - Smartphone 64GB, 4GB RAM, Dual Sim, Navy Blue</h4>
                <div class="counter"> 
                  <div class="btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-minus"></i></i></div>
                  <span class=number>0</span>
                 <div class="btn">
                   <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-plus"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="price">
                  <div class="amount">$ 50.00</div>
                
                </div>
                <div class="remove-button"><button type="button" class="remove">Borrar</button></div>
            </div>
          </article>
          </template>

          
        <!-- fin template carrito -->
          <section class="discount-checkout">
            <article class="article-margin-padding discount">
              <div>
                <h3 class="discount-code">Codigo de Descuento</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="discount-container">
                <form>
                  <label for="discount">
                    <input class="discount-box" type="text" name="discount" id="discount-input" />
                  </label>
                    <input class="discount-button" type="submit" id="discount-button" value="Aplicar"/>
                </form>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="article-margin-padding checkout">
              <div class="subtotal-box">
                <div class="flex-grow-70"><h4 class="subtotal">Subtotal</h4></div>
                <div><h4 class="price-total" id="subtotal">0</h4></div>
              </div>
              <div class="subtotal-box discount-code-box" id="discount-code-box">
                <div class="flex-grow-70"><h4 class="subtotal h4-discount">Codigo de Descuento</h4></div>
                <div><h4 class="price-total" id="discount">0</h4></div>
              </div>
              <div class="total-box">
                <div class="flex-grow-70"><h4 class="total">Total</h4></div>
                <div><h4 class="price-total" id="total">0</h4></div>
              </div>
              <div action="product/checkout" class="checkout-buttom">
                <form class="card-body" id="checkoutCart">
                  <div class="row checkout">
                    <div class=" col-md-6 mb-4 tipoenvio">
                      <!-- <div class="select-sender">
                        Elija un tipo de envio.
                    </div> -->
                        <label class="tipoEnvio" for="country">Tipo Envio</label>
                        <select class="custom-select d-block w-100" id="shippingMethod" name=" shippingMethod"
                            required="">
                            <option value="">Elegir...</option>
                            <option value="Cadete">Cadete</option>
                            <option value="Correo">Correo Argentino</option>
                            <option value="Andreani">Andreani</option>
                            <option value="DHL">DHL</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class=" col-md-6 mb-4">
                      <!-- <div class="select-payment">
                        Elija un Medio de Pago.
                    </div> -->
                        <label class="formaPago" for="country">Pago</label>
                        <select class="custom-select d-block w-100" id="paymentMethod" name="paymentMethod"
                            required="">
                            <option value="">Elegir...</option>
                            <option value="Efectivo">Efectivo</option>
                            <option value="Débito">Tarjeta Débito</option>
                            <option value="Crédito">Tarjeta Crédito</option>
                        </select>
                       
    
                    </div>
                </div>
          
                <button type="submit" id="checkoutCart">Finalizar Compra</button>

                </form>
              </div>
              <div class="checkout-continue"><button onclick="location.href='product'">Continuar Comprando</button></div>              
            </article>
            
          </section>
          
            <div class="suggestion suggestion-title-box">
              <h2 class="suggestion-title">A personas como tu le interesaron los siguientes productos</h2>
            </div>       
           
          <section class="section-set-display sección01">
            <div class="swiper mySwiper seccion1">
              <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              <% for (i = 0; i < searchedProducts.length; i++) { %> 
              <div class="swiper-slide bckSwiper">
                 <article class="article-style bckArticle">
                   <div class="bckCard seccion1">
                     </div>
                   <div class="imgProduct seccion1">
                   <img onclick="location.href='product/productDetail/<%= searchedProducts[i].id%>'"
                      src="images/products/<%= searchedProducts[i].image_product %>" 
                      alt="<%= searchedProducts[i].name %>"/>
                   </div>
                  
    
                   <div class="descriptionProduct seccion1">  
                   <div class="title seccion1">
                     <h5><%= searchedProducts[i].name %></h5>
                   </div>               
                   </div>
                          
            
                </article>
              </div>
    
         
          
            <% } %>
              </div>
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
             </div>
          </section>
         
        </main>
        <footer>
          <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-logo"><a href="/home" target="_blank" title="Principal"><img src="/images/logoFooter.png" alt="Logo-TecnoMundo"></a></div>
            <div><h6>Al comprar se aceptan los <a class="tyc" href="#"> Términos y Condiciones</a></h6></div>
            <div><h5>Copyright 2022 | Todos los derechos reservados Tecnomundo.com. Tecnomundo S.A.C.I. e I. | Mendoza | Argentina</h5></div>
            <div><p>Las fotos son a modo ilustrativo. La venta de cualquiera de los productos publicados está sujeta a la verificación de stock. Los precios online y los planes de financiación para los productos presentados/publicados en www.fravega.com.ar y/o www.fravega.com son válidos exclusivamente para la compra vía internet en las páginas antes mencionadas. Las especificaciones técnicas y descripciones están sujetas a cambios sin previo aviso.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="data-fiscal-container"><a href="https://www.afip.gob.ar" target="_blank" title="AFIP"><img src="images/data-fiscal.jpg" alt="data-fiscal"/></a></div>
        </footer>
        <script src="/js/productCart.js"></script>
          <!-- Swiper JS -->

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Initialize Swiper -->
    <script>
      var swiper = new Swiper(".mySwiper", {
        slidesPerView: 1,
        spaceBetween: 0,
        loop: true,
        freeMode: true,
        pagination: {
          el: ".swiper-pagination",
          clickable: true,
        },
        breakpoints: {
          361: {
            slidesPerView: 2,
            spaceBetween: 10,
          },
          600: {
            slidesPerView: 3,
            spaceBetween: 20,
          },
          // 700: {
          //   slidesPerView: 4,
          //   spaceBetween: 10,
          // },
          761: {
            slidesPerView: 4,
            spaceBetween: 15,
          },
          900: {
            slidesPerView: 5,
            spaceBetween: 15,
          },
        }
      });
    </script>
    </body>
    
</html>